{"tid":2319321,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"今次要到熱刺空難死全家......................","createTime":"2020-12-10T04:25:30.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-10T07:59:22.000Z","uid":119729,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"46b33362e955b8e5785a8968ea4fe317f195ec38","tid":2319321,"uid":119729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:25:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=31651118136\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsports.now.com%2Fhome%2Fnews%2Fdetails%3Fid%3D31651118136&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=ed2fbbd4\" target=\"_blank\">https://sports.now.com/home/news/details?id=31651118136</a><br />\n<br />\n孫興敏甩手 巴爾戲言：卡列斯！<br />\n<br />\n【Now Sports】熱刺球星加利夫巴爾認真夠幽默，操練看到孫興敏接波帥手，竟大叫卡列斯的名字，該德國門將則無辜再受奚落。<br />\n英超榜首球隊熱刺士氣高昂，周三操練備戰周四歐霸盃時也不乏輕鬆愉快的場面，韓國球星孫興敏一次接波甩手，在旁觀看的加利夫巴爾（Gareth Bale）竟叫出：「卡列斯」（Loris Karius）的名字，惹得現場笑聲一片。<br />\n<br />\n2017/18年歐聯決賽，卡列斯為利物浦把關對皇家馬德里，加利夫巴爾40碼外一個遠射，卡列斯竟然把波拍入網中，結果導致紅軍以1:3大敗。那場比賽也成為紅軍和卡列斯永遠的痛。<br />\n<br />\n不過，巴爾和卡列斯如今命運相似，大家都因缺乏狀態而成為後備兵，當然愛打高爾夫球的巴爾心理質素比卡列斯好，不論是否當後備都照樣享受人生。<br />\n<br />\n相關片段：<br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/TheSpursExpress/status/1336714749451624450\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheSpursExpress%2Fstatus%2F1336714749451624450&d=DJHqE1tJ5F0S1%2BmpD1KYpgRqNnYsekRkiG%2Fa4%2F0EtZc%3D&h=932f0534\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FTheSpursExpress%2Fstatus%2F1336714749451624450&h=38e11e4f\" target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/TheSpursExpress/status/1336714749451624450</a>"},{"pid":"b587fe090a5a4a7d81c9284a631ffcfe27edb3ec","tid":2319321,"uid":21896,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:29:48.000Z","msg":"咁bale又真係狗左啲既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不過幾好笑"},{"pid":"3ce89f6df675cc7e4c348d21aed9ed797794b259","tid":2319321,"uid":218659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,